data.description: Here is your chance to own a remodeled home in one of the sought-after quiet neighborhood of Schaumburg, known with highly rated schools.  It has a gleaming hardwood floors throughout the main level, and tile floorings throughout the lower level including the laundry area with washer and dryer.  The main bathroom was totally updated, and has an updated kitchen with granite counter tops that comes with stainless steel refrigerator, stove/oven and dishwasher.  Along with the remodeling done in 2022, the sellers also replaced the electrical panel.  Besides the recent updates on this home, you will enjoy relaxing in the very spacious backyard with a large 2 Tier deck and fenced backyard, perfect for big outdoor barbecue party.  The above ground pool which adds more family & friends enjoyment and entertainment can remain or remove by the sellers at the buyers option.  This property is also perfectly located near I-390, shopping centers, Metra station and public parks.  In addition, this property also comes with an energy saving solar panels that can save you a lot of money on your monthly electric bill.
